rows.label: tlk001901_09_msg0001
rows.name:
I heard Acedia's no more. What in the
world is happening to Alst?

rows.label: tlk001901_09_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm sure you've things you need to
do, and this goes without saying, but
just...be careful, will you?

rows.label: tlk001901_09_msg0003
rows.name:
And when this is all over...well, I know
this isn't the most happening of places,
but I hope you'll come back to visit us.

rows.label: tlk001901_09_msg0005
rows.name:
Take care out there.
We'll be waiting for you.

rows.label: tlk001901_09_msg0006
rows.name: I will. And of course I'll come back.

rows.label: tlk001901_09_msg0007
rows.name:
Well then, you can look forward to
a big plate of Acqua Pearl Pazza
when you come home!

rows.label: tlk001901_09_msg0008
rows.name:
Don't you dare let your Auntie Correl
down now!
